law.history: Repealed 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 188, sec. 69, effective December 1, 1972. -- Amended 1968 Ky. Acts ch. 152, sec. 93, effective June 13, 1968. -- Amended 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 169, secs. 2 and 4. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs 1482, 1482b, 1483, 1593a -5.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Return of keys to ballot boxes, stub books and ballots -- Preservation and disposal of election papers.
